cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the preamble received target power to an invalid value of 999 will cause random access power control errors and prevent UE initial access.
du.explanation_zh: 將前導接收目標功率設定為無效值 999 會導致隨機接入功率控制錯誤，並阻止 UE 初始接入。
